【Excellent Performance】The solid state drive is silent, shock-proof, drop-proof and shock-proof, so you don't have to worry even if the computer falls. EDILOCA ES106 makes your game load times faster and gets the near-instant performance and gaming fun that solid-state storage brings.

【3D NAND】EDILOCA ES106 adopts advanced 3D NAND technology, and the components are carefully designed from start to finish. With SATA III 6Gb/S interface, the read speed can reach up to 550Mb/s, and the write speed can reach up to 450Mb/s, which greatly improves the performance and efficiency of your computer. 【Warranty Service】EDILOCA has 3 year warranty service. We have strict control standards for our products, each hard drive has been tested countless times to ensure that there is no quality problem before sending it to you. If you have any questions about the product, you can contact us at any time. We will give you the most sincere service.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 1, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I bought this SSD to perk up an older laptop with a SATA II port with a rather slow hard drive. After installing, I did some benchmarking on the drive. I am getting read and write speeds very close to what is given in the description, which are about 10 times what the original HDD did, and about as high as any SATA II SSD I've seen. Where it took a particular Linux distro over a minute to load before, it now only takes about 12 seconds and, of course, part of that time is the BIOS loading.I don't know how long this drive will last, but it sure lives up to it's speed specs and at an excellent price.
